import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter as Router,Routes,Route} from 'react-router-dom'

import Home from ''
function App() {
  return (
   <Router>
    <Routes>
     <Route  path="/"  element={<Home/>}/>
    <Route exact path="/login"  element={<Login/>}/>
    <Route  path="/signup"  element={<Signup/>}/>
    </Routes>
   </Router>
  )
}

export default App
